high_descs: Begin walking over to the sink, then turn right and walk up to the wall, turn left to walk over to the rightmost sink.
Pick up the blue spray bottle that is to the right of the sink.
Turn around and walk over to the toilet, then turn around to face the sink again.
Open the cabinet door that is second from the right below the sink, place the blue spray bottle inside, then close the door.
Turn around and walk over to the toilet.
Pick up the blue spray bottle that is resting on top of the toilet tank.
Turn around and take a step towards the sink counter.
Open the cabinet door that is second from the right, place the blue spray bottle inside to the left of the bottle that is already in there and close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles into a cabinet.

high_descs: turn right and head over to the end of the room, then turn left once you're there and walk to the right side of the bathroom cabinets
grab a spray bottle off of the bathroom cabinet coutertop
back up a bit so that you can open the cabinet below the sink
place the spray bottle inside the bottom left cabinet
turn around to face the toilet
grab the spray bottle off of the top of the toilet
turn around to face the bathroom sink cabinet again
place the spray bottle in the bottom left cabinet
anns.task_desc: place two spray bottles in the bathroom cabinet

high_descs: Walk slightly up, turn to the right and then turn to the left to the sink.
Pick up the blue spray bottle on top of the counter top.
Go to the cabinet underneath the sink.
Open the cabinet, put the spray bottle in it and close the cabinet.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Pick up another blue spray bottle on top of the water tank.
Turn around and go to the cabinet underneath the sink again.
Put the spray bottle next to the other bottle in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put 2 blue spray bottles inside the cabinet underneath the sink.
